ventral branch of embolus.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6683477" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6683477" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6683477/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="426" startId="3.[151,250,1925,1949]" targetBox="[151,1436,1184,1901]" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1436,1925,2021]" pageId="3" pageNumber="426">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,278,1925,1949]" pageId="3" pageNumber="426">FIGURE 3.</emphasis>
Epigyne and vulva of 
<taxonomicName authority="(Roewer, 1960)" authorityName="Zamani &amp; Marusik" authorityYear="2022" baseAuthorityName="Roewer" baseAuthorityYear="1960" box="[522,910,1925,1949]" class="Arachnida" family="Zodariidae" genus="Indozodion" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="3" pageNumber="426" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="lindbergi">
<emphasis box="[522,737,1925,1949]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="426">Indozodion lindbergi</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Roewer, C. F." box="[753,903,1925,1949]" pageId="3" pageNumber="426" pagination="1 - 53" refId="ref6705" refString="Roewer, C. F. (1960) Solifugen und Opilioniden - Araneae Orthognathae, Haplogynae und Entelegynae (Contribution a l'etude de la faune d'Afghanistan 23). Goteborgs Kungliga Vetenskaps och Vitterhets Samhalles Handlingar, Series 6, B 8 (7), 1 - 53." type="journal article" year="1960">Roewer, 1960</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. A macerated epigyne, ventral; B vulva, dorsal; C intact epigyne, ventral; D right receptacle, dorsal; E left receptacle, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.2 mm. Abbreviations: 
<emphasis box="[1276,1328,1961,1984]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="426">Oc—</emphasis>
